name: The 12 Days of Christmas by Kelly O'Gorman, pack of 5 x A5 cards
description:
I usually create a calendar at the end of the year but this year I've decided to draw some Christmas cards.
Based on the song 'The 12 days of Christmas', these cards are A5 in size and come in a pack of 5.
They are blank inside for your own personalisation.

Thanks to all those Facebook people who helped to submit ideas for the lords a leaping!

20% of the purchase price goes to The Childrens Liver Disease Foundation.

They can also be brought from the shop 'Barnet Belle' in Barnet
www.barnetbelle.com

If your country is not in the postage list, please let me know and I will add it, many thanks! x

name: 'Flora' Limited Edition Signed Print by Kelly O'Gorman
description:
A Limited Edition Signed Print of 50 
Flora is a black and white ink drawing inspired by nature,her name says it all! This picture has become the inspiration for a new body of work, which I am currently working on.

There are options to have this framed or unframed.
Flora measures 420mm x 290mm (without the frame)

If this picture is being sent in the post, 'plexiglass', an acrylic alternative to glass will be used.

There is an option to collect the picture from Barnet Belle, a shop in Barnet, directions can be found here www.barnetbelle.com, If you wish to do this then please contact me and I can give you a code to remove the postage.
